{"tid":489298,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美斯銅像再次被毀","createTime":"2017-12-04T14:09:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-05T10:27:04.000Z","uid":16659,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f893ffe3b884f9ea871cea0043f569dbf42fd3ea","tid":489298,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:09:07.000Z","msg":"球王都有對頭人！位於阿根廷布宜諾斯艾利斯的美斯銅像，繼今年1月後再次被毀，整個倒在地上，但暫時未知「兇手」誰屬。<br />\n<br />\n位於布宜諾斯艾利斯Costanera Sur公園裡的美斯銅像，與阿根廷多位體壇名將的銅像例如網球手Gabriela Sabatini、Guillermo Vilas和NBA球星真奴比利等放在一起，但唯獨美斯的銅像特別不受歡迎，在今年初被「斬頭斬身」後，日前它又被斬斷雙腳，整個跌在地上，暫時未有人就毀壞事件作出回應。<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.performgroup.com/di/library/GOAL/ae/3a/messi-statue_s45qbgxyafxl1fsz9frcf7sxz.jpg?t=553751648\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.performgroup.com%2Fdi%2Flibrary%2FGOAL%2Fae%2F3a%2Fmessi-statue_s45qbgxyafxl1fsz9frcf7sxz.jpg%3Ft%3D553751648&h=5a53b463&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"588b652caa6913c180b245b799cc1e46902e7f77","tid":489298,"uid":35587,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:09:37.000Z","msg":"一入黎笑左"},{"pid":"7e19e12cfced9373d7cd8e18e9a1b53cedbf34b9","tid":489298,"uid":5649,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:10:09.000Z","msg":"美斯斷腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1576ab62a11a0feaf135008b787cd807fcfa4efc","tid":489298,"uid":109983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:11:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8e5f52e71ae88f65f4798a7635bc35a2323245b","tid":489298,"uid":99364,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:17:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ff2b2d33883b0d4cd6702d8ddc8ef209b1dacff","tid":489298,"uid":9115