if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cb6e35b85209dfc150190db5891bad6b2107498","tid":489298,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:41:32.000Z","msg":"美斯雕像又被「分屍」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/0/960/19694527960/19695681063_600x337.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F0%2F960%2F19694527960%2F19695681063_600x337.jpg&h=d8e902bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=e00X04FWOkacxl1y7xrdRUjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=ee1f2baf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】阿根廷球王美斯在國內一家大受歡迎，萬人景仰？未必！<br />\n<br />\n不少成功球星在所屬球會或國家都被立有雕像，而在阿根廷首都布宜諾斯艾利斯的體壇星光大道，於2016年6月就樹立了美斯（Lionel Messi）的雕像。<br />\n<br />\n不過，動作是美斯正在帶球突破的雕像，在周日被人破壞，兩隻腳從腳踭位置被切斷，而上身則跌落在地上，「分屍死狀」十分恐怖！<br />\n<br />\n今次已不是這個美斯雕像第1次被破壞，在今年1月也曾被「分屍」，但手法不同，是從腰部分成上下一半。警方在2次都未能找到「兇手」。<br />\n<br />\n雖然美斯在巴塞隆拿贏盡一切，但未能把如此好表現帶到阿根廷國家隊，至今從未贏得任何國際賽冠軍，因此他在國內有支持者也有批評者。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : Twitter圖片"},{"pid":"cda8af8048bc2b3c3713c2aa289c2d2e6b612be4","tid":489298,"uid":34490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:43:11.000Z","msg":"忍唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2398dc407e19ac9231adb19fffbb5469d81faf9b","tid":489298,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:43:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>美斯斷腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吊你貢黑心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n看圖講故事"},{"pid":"43627f6ce54da1339480b1998c55d9d3ec4e3d02","tid":489298,"uid":40757,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"repl